{"tid":1243603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老母越戰時期分享如何應對美軍","createTime":"2019-06-19T14:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T14:46:42.000Z","uid":58841,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f2395f21603591454af6b7443fa728d84b56f5e","tid":1243603,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:01:39.000Z","msg":"老母係我呢個年紀岩岩好打緊杖<br />\n日日返學都要警惕有冇美軍係天上面掟粒彈同地下有冇地雷<br />\n作為手無寸鐵既佢每次返學就要準備幾樣野<br />\n<br />\n1.外套<br />\n唔好睇小件嬲 佢係保護自己既最佳裝備<br />\n可擋彈可擋亂棍攻擊<br />\n最好要同附近環境顏色相近 有咩E郁即刻搵地方匿<br />\n老母個陣係將成堆稻草cover落自己個身<br />\n一路保護細妹一路搵地洞捐入去<br />\n<br />\n2.毛巾同蘇打水<br />\n唔好諗住戴口罩就避到<br />\n老母以前食煙係即刻搵水濕住毛巾um住個鼻黎走<br />\n<br />\n3.保護鏡<br />\n呢個就唔多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：老母戰神"},{"pid":"ef8c37eaecfffe3e8f7271551f5cc1a4719a5c45","tid":1243603,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1f9e81cdb9de22c67a0505b91d1dc99b4c8c3a","tid":1243603,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:06:04.000Z","msg":"結論：兒子弱智"},{"pid":"9aa4a1d76370d09a196316f81f9befbd2ca91852","tid":1243603,"uid":58841,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"ef8c37eaecfffe3e8f7271551f5cc1a4719a5c45","tid":1243603,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:09:06.000Z","msg":"你係咪未聽過高齡產婦"},{"pid":"c44d811f4eeb4e8e3fe143e97cae07b3976453a3","tid":1243603,"uid":225295,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9aa4a1d76370d09a196316f81f9befbd2ca91852","tid":1243603,"uid":58841,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"ef8c37eaecfffe3e8f7271551f5cc1a4719a5c45","tid":1243603,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06